query:
SELECT 
  moduleNumber,
  title,
  youtubeVideoId,
  CASE 
    WHEN youtubeVideoId = 'PLACEHOLDER' THEN 'MISSING'
    ELSE 'HAS VIDEO'
  END as video_status,
  CHAR_LENGTH(transcriptContent) as transcript_length,
  CASE 
    WHEN transcriptContent IS NULL THEN 'MISSING'
    WHEN transcriptContent LIKE '%PLACEHOLDER%' THEN 'PLACEHOLDER'
    WHEN CHAR_LENGTH(transcriptContent) < 200 THEN 'TOO SHORT'
    ELSE 'COMPLETE'
  END as transcript_status
FROM modules
ORDER BY moduleNumber
